    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait really? that sounds scary. i dont want to stop my meds though coz i dont want to have an episode. if i just drink like 4 or 5 liters of water a day and take some extra ibuprofen for the headache, can i just ride it out at home? it's pretty late and the clinics are closed anyway i can just wait till monday?",
